snippet.title: Telefrag VR – Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready for the battle? Telefrag VR's arena is now open on Steam, Oculus and PlayStation VR!

Steam ▪ http://bit.ly/Telefrag_Steam
Oculus ▪ http://bit.ly/Telefrag_Oculus
PlayStation US ▪ http://bit.ly/Telefrag_PlayStation_US
PlayStation EU ▪ http://bit.ly/Telefrag_PlayStation_EU

Compete on 5 unique arenas: Fallen Champion, Mobius Villa, Lazarus Grotto, Imperial Shipyard and The Six Leagues Under. Each of them will give you a completely different experience, but above all, many challenges. We put in your hands a full arsenal of destruction, inspired by the legendary tools of extermination from the classic 90's FPS games: Particle Cannon, Laser Pistol, Plasma Rifle, Flak Cannon, Rocket Launcher. Pick the best loadouts, conquer the enemies, and finally make a name for yourself - The Champion.

---
